Something we can drink to.

00:35.774 --> 00:40.561
All right, this one I... I... I played
for a rosy-cheeked lady named Elsa.

00:40.562 --> 00:42.113
ALL: To Elsa!

00:42.114 --> 00:44.949
Uh-uh-uh... To Thor Gundersen!

00:44.950 --> 00:46.567
ALL: To Thor Gundersen!

