GUARD: That sound you, shithead, hmm?

02:32.106 --> 02:35.023
- GOODWIN: No. (WHIMPERING)
- His name is...

02:35.024 --> 02:38.343
Is Private James Goodwin.

02:42.582 --> 02:44.666
Oh, when you address me, it's sir,

02:44.667 --> 02:46.334
you goddamn Swedish bastard.

02:46.335 --> 02:47.819
Norwegian, sir.

02:50.290 --> 02:52.223
Goddamn Norwegian bastard, sir.

02:57.430 --> 02:59.481
The Swede's got jokes.

02:59.482 --> 03:01.333
Yeah. (CHUCKLES)

03:04.138 --> 03:05.270
Ah...

03:06.939 --> 03:08.573
Jokes and contraband.

03:10.810 --> 03:13.545
Maybe the Swede should play me a song.

03:16.783 --> 03:17.915
Mmm-hmm.

03:29.996 --> 03:34.365
I said play me a song, Swede.

03:35.435 --> 03:39.854
My name is Thor Gundersen from Norway.

03:39.855 --> 03:42.307
