04:19.293 --> 04:20.611
Here we go.

04:21.313 --> 04:24.231
Swede, I'm the one
that feeds him, Swede.

04:24.232 --> 04:25.717
I'm the one that feeds him.

04:26.352 --> 04:28.885
- (WHIPPING)
- (YELLING) I'm the one.

04:29.622 --> 04:31.254
I'm the one that feeds him.

04:31.790 --> 04:33.573
Do you hear me, Swede?

04:33.574 --> 04:34.892
I'm the one.

04:38.696 --> 04:40.663
