04:42.768 --> 04:45.168
(WHIMPERING, MOANING)

04:48.473 --> 04:50.706
(CRYING)

04:51.243 --> 04:53.693
- (GRUNTING)
- James, look at me, James.

04:53.694 --> 04:55.161
Look at me.

04:55.162 --> 04:58.547
I am your friend, Thor Gundersen.

04:58.950 --> 05:00.416
(YELLING, GRUNTING)

05:00.919 --> 05:02.468
It is me.

05:02.469 --> 05:05.121
- It is... It is me!
- (GROWLING)

05:05.590 --> 05:07.657
- Look at me, James.
- (GRUNTING)

05:08.493 --> 05:11.161
It is me. I am your friend.

05:11.797 --> 05:13.946
- I am your friend.
- (MUFFLED SCREAMING)

05:13.947 --> 05:15.197
It is me.

05:16.801 --> 05:18.466
Thor Gundersen.

05:19.603 --> 05:20.602
It is me.

05:24.975 --> 05:27.442
I am your friend.

05:32.516 --> 05:33.849
(VERY SOFTLY) It is me.

05:35.519 --> 05:37.619
