31:04.668 --> 31:06.100
(GRUNTING)

31:19.749 --> 31:20.915
(GUNSHOT)

31:26.223 --> 31:27.689
Prisoner...

31:50.346 --> 31:51.978
(THE SWEDE GRUNTING)

32:02.258 --> 32:03.990
(HEAVY BREATHING)

32:10.799 --> 32:12.065
(STRAINING)

32:28.383 --> 32:30.016
Thank you, devil.

32:37.692 --> 32:39.192
(FOOTSTEPS APPROACHING)

32:43.932 --> 32:45.131
(GUNS COCKING)

33:20.023 --> 33:22.223
(SNIPPING)

33:23.193 --> 33:24.459
(TEARING)

33:59.662 --> 34:01.395
(SQUELCHING)

34:05.000 --> 34:05.999
(DRIPPING)

34:11.338 --> 34:13.103
(SCREAMING)

34:15.579 --> 34:17.244
(COUGHING)

34:20.917 --> 34:23.016
(SCREAMING CONTINUES)

34:28.592 --> 34:29.591
(METAL CLINKS)

34:31.327 --> 34:33.260
(SCREAMING)

34:33.661 --> 34:34.962
(COUGHING)

34:35.197 --> 34:37.130
(SCREAMING CONTINUES)

34:53.382 --> 34:54.382
(METAL CLINKS)

35:23.579 --> 35:24.588
(INHALES THROUGH TEETH)

35:24.589 --> 35:26.080
I thought you gave up the ghost.

35:27.382 --> 35:28.515
(GROANING)

35:36.391 --> 35:38.642
(GROANING)

35:38.643 --> 35:40.343
You'll be all right.

35:40.344 --> 35:42.278
That bullet shattered.

35:42.279 --> 35:44.397
(SIGHS) Shrapnel all through your thigh.

35:45.067 --> 35:48.168
Extracted a few fragments, but
there's still some deep inside.

35:49.203 --> 35:50.603
Here you go.

35:51.606 --> 35:52.805
I want it out.

35:54.175 --> 35:55.791
All of it.

35:55.792 --> 35:58.310
It's part of you now. You'll be carrying
it around for the rest of your life.

36:02.528 --> 36:04.317
Hmm. How long I been here?

36:04.318 --> 36:05.651
Four days.

36:07.121 --> 36:08.353
(GROANING)

36:12.927 --> 36:14.827
(GRUNTS)

36:17.331 --> 36:20.066
The man I brought in here. Gundersen?

36:21.669 --> 36:23.019
Yeah.

36:23.020 --> 36:26.238
Captain sent a few riders out to
that homestead you told us about.

36:27.541 --> 36:29.324
(SIGHS)

36:29.325 --> 36:32.194
Circuit judge come out from Salt Lake.

36:32.195 --> 36:33.778
We had us a trial yesterday.

36:35.216 --> 36:36.648
He hand down a judgment?

36:38.051 --> 36:39.251
He did.

36:40.921 --> 36:42.904
(HARMONICA PLAYING)

36:42.905 --> 36:44.189
(SHUDDERS)

36:51.599 --> 36:52.731
(GASPS)

36:54.968 --> 36:56.502
(HEAVY BREATHING)

37:10.082 --> 37:11.449
Excuse me.

37:13.586 --> 37:14.985
(GRUNTS)

37:15.721 --> 37:16.987
Excuse me.

37:18.791 --> 37:20.641
Private, what...

37:20.642 --> 37:22.142
What is that...

37:22.143 --> 37:23.761
What is that you're playing?

37:24.430 --> 37:25.596
(GRUNTS)

37:34.006 --> 37:35.639
It got no name far as I know.

37:37.209 --> 37:39.543
Just a melody I keep hearing in my head.

37:40.245 --> 37:44.414
It is not "just a melody"

37:45.584 --> 37:48.018
rattling around in your head, you.

37:50.489 --> 37:55.059
It is, unless I misheard, <i>Two Soldiers,</i>

37:56.261 --> 37:57.728
and you...

37:59.198 --> 38:00.731
You almost have it,

38:02.601 --> 38:06.620
but for blowing a note or two,

38:06.621 --> 38:08.171
you should be drawing.

38:12.210 --> 38:15.878
A more intimate instrument
does not exist.

38:17.949 --> 38:19.148
You...

38:20.451 --> 38:27.223
You give to it the most
cherished gift a man has...

38:28.626 --> 38:30.093
His breath, hmm?

38:32.097 --> 38:34.897
You release into it your...

38:37.435 --> 38:38.968
Your very soul.

38:43.073 --> 38:45.274
The best players,

38:47.445 --> 38:49.044
for a moment, they touch God.

38:51.315 --> 38:52.848
I can show you.

38:56.053 --> 38:57.286
Eat your food.

38:58.088 --> 38:59.755
I am...

39:03.794 --> 39:05.761
I was a musician.

39:10.568 --> 39:12.100
That's your last food.

39:12.936 --> 39:14.069
(STUTTERING)

39:17.240 --> 39:18.973
(HEAVY BREATHING)

39:24.080 --> 39:25.079
(GRUNTS)

39:28.217 --> 39:29.917
(HEAVY BREATHING)

39:32.789 --> 39:34.822
(MUTTERING)

39:37.226 --> 39:38.959
(GRUNTING IN PAIN)

39:44.100 --> 39:47.534
Thank you, thee, oh, Lord,

39:48.437 --> 39:52.273
for this bounty you have
placed before me...

39:53.209 --> 39:54.474
Hmm.

39:55.111 --> 39:56.811
(INHALES SHARPLY)

39:58.080 --> 40:00.181
(HEAVY BREATHING, GRUNTING)

40:03.186 --> 40:04.819
(FOOTSTEPS APPROACHING)

40:09.491 --> 40:10.624
(CULLEN GRUNTS)

40:18.367 --> 40:21.167
(GRUNTING)

40:24.973 --> 40:26.940
(HEAVY BREATHING)

40:29.711 --> 40:35.781
Mother gave me a harmonica
on my tenth birthday.

40:39.054 --> 40:43.957
"A man who can make music will
never be lonely," she said.

40:49.616 --> 40:51.683
Hanged by the neck until dead.

40:56.703 --> 40:57.836
You...

40:58.505 --> 41:00.538
You are a merciful man,

41:02.209 --> 41:03.675
Mr. Bohannon.

41:06.247 --> 41:07.645
Thought I was the devil.

41:11.718 --> 41:13.252
I was wrong.

41:16.423 --> 41:17.789
You are just a man.

41:20.794 --> 41:22.727
Just a man. A man of war.

41:24.031 --> 41:28.333
War made both of us, after all.

41:31.712 --> 41:33.678
Ain't no way out of this one, Swede.

41:34.648 --> 41:37.015
No. The way out is...

41:38.119 --> 41:41.286
Is by your... Your hand.

41:44.492 --> 41:48.693
One act of forgiveness
is... Is all I ask.

41:49.096 --> 41:52.264
One act of mercy.

41:55.536 --> 41:57.936
(STUTTERS) I do not want to hang.

42:02.643 --> 42:04.142
I ain't your maker.

42:04.944 --> 42:07.061
(WHIMPERING, STUTTERING)

42:07.367 --> 42:09.885
Forgive me, Cullen.

42:12.289 --> 42:13.789
(STUTTERING) Forgive me.

42:17.061 --> 42:18.527
(HEAVY BREATHING)

42:24.401 --> 42:26.836
Forgive yourself, huh?

42:37.348 --> 42:39.547
- PRIVATE: It's time.
- (THE SWEDE GASPING)

42:41.952 --> 42:43.918
Oh! (HEAVY BREATHING)

42:54.447 --> 42:57.206
God have mercy upon your soul.

43:02.989 --> 43:04.322
(THE SWEDE GRUNTS)

43:16.647 --> 43:19.949
(FLAG FLUTTERING)

43:45.873 --> 43:48.340
"Thor Gundersen, late of Salt Lake City,

43:49.443 --> 43:52.227
not having the fear of
God before your eyes,

43:52.228 --> 43:55.513
but being moved and seduced by
the instigation of the devil,

43:56.117 --> 43:59.868
have been found guilty of
feloniously and willfully

43:59.869 --> 44:01.937
with malice aforethought

44:01.938 --> 44:06.274
of depriving Aaron Hatch
and Sara Hatch of life

44:06.275 --> 44:08.927
so that they then and
there instantly died.

44:11.732 --> 44:13.365
The sentence is death.

44:14.034 --> 44:16.501
You shall be hanged by
the neck until dead."

44:17.738 --> 44:19.153
(PAPER RUSTLING)

44:19.154 --> 44:20.772
May the Lord have mercy upon your soul.

44:24.144 --> 44:25.744
(EXHALING HEAVILY)

44:37.591 --> 44:39.758
(BREATHING HEAVILY)

44:44.798 --> 44:48.132
Uh, no, not this. Please, not this...
I ca... Please, please.

44:59.378 --> 45:01.045
CAPTAIN PAULSON:
Have you any last words?

45:01.781 --> 45:03.747
(HEAVY BREATHING)

45:12.591 --> 45:18.796
I am Thor Gundersen.

45:22.068 --> 45:24.434
From Norway.

45:25.804 --> 45:27.070
Hmm.

45:31.343 --> 45:33.243
- (CREAKING)
- (THE SWEDE GASPING)

45:37.449 --> 45:39.582
(GAGGING)

45:48.260 --> 45:50.560
(COUGHING)

45:56.501 --> 45:58.601
(GRUNTING)

46:04.075 --> 46:06.642
(GAGGING)

46:07.945 --> 46:09.612
(GRUNTS)

46:25.897 --> 46:27.129
(THE SWEDE GASPS)

46:52.489 --> 46:54.156
- (CREAKING)
- (URINATING)

47:16.980 --> 47:18.346
(BREATHING HEAVILY)

47:45.842 --> 47:46.974
He's dead.

48:58.980 --> 49:01.548
(GRUNTS)

